Subject: [PATCH 080/155] f2fs: factor out a f2fs_map_no_dnode

Factor out a helper to return a hole when no dnode was found.

Signed-off-by: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Reviewed-by: Chao Yu <chao@kernel.org>
